{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/grafana/awesome-k6/readme","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c9eafca2-4c4d-5ddd-afad-f7bad5d95606","html":"<div align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://k6.io/\">\n    <img src=\"https://github.com/grafana/awesome-k6/raw/main/assets/bert.png\" alt=\"k6 mascot\" width=\"300px\">\n  </a></div>\n<!--lint disable awesome-heading--><html><head></head><body>\n<h1 id=\"awesome-k6-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-k6-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome k6 awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome k6 <a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<!--lint enable awesome-heading--><html><head></head><body>\n<p>A collection of content by the community, on (testing with) <a href=\"https://k6.io/\"></a>k6.</p>\n<p>Want to help in making this list better? Yay, that's awesome! Before you get started though, please have a look at our <a href=\"https://github.com/grafana/awesome-k6/blob/main/code_of_conduct.md\">code of conduct</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/grafana/awesome-k6/blob/main/contributing.md\">contribution guidelines</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><